      "title": "A heatwave cartoon for New Scientist.",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/17d1bd3f4bee811a2df25fa9b5f30ebb/36bd6d07a402aa10-bc/s640x960/fb0b9d01bd8bdc2ff17dc54aa0cf787713f82017.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"1209\" data-orig-width=\"1800\" alt=\"1. Title: The North Wind and the Sun quarrelled as to who was the stronger. &#10;&#10;2. The Sun says: &quot;I propose a wager: See yonder traveller, let us see who can make him remove his cloak.&quot;&#10;&#10;3. The northwind blows on the traveller, the sun says: &quot;You blow yet he only wraps it tighter!&quot;&#10;&#10;4. The sun shines on the traveller, saying: Observe! . The traveller mutters &quot;nice and warm&quot;&#10;&#10;5. The Sun says &quot;See, my kindness brought results!&quot; The traveller has removed hos cloak and begins to sweat. &quot;Fair enough, you win.&quot; concedes the North Wind.&#10;&#10;6. &quot;Tremble before my gracious heat!&quot; says the sun, smiling bradly. His heat has started a fire. the traveller flees. The North Wind says &quot;I think that&#xE2;&#x80;&#x99;s enough.&quot;&#10;&#10;7. &quot;Let the world burn with my cleansing benevolence!!&quot; blazes the sun madly, now grown huge in the sky. The land is a burning fireball. &quot;Now you&#xE2;&#x80;&#x99;re scaring me!&quot; says the North Wind anxiously.&#10;\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/17d1bd3f4bee811a2df25fa9b5f30ebb/36bd6d07a402aa10-bc/s75x75_c1/0cfa0dc73178d99ef4f8e47b8524c4f8e8d010ad.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/17d1bd3f4bee811a2df25fa9b5f30ebb/36bd6d07a402aa10-bc/s100x200/fe94b61054c30342f1d34d0d49137dbfe51b30b0.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/17d1bd3f4bee811a2df25fa9b5f30ebb/36bd6d07a402aa10-bc/s250x400/09627a5dc6af3b69e5ad581cda83dcbfe268904b.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/17d1bd3f4bee811a2df25fa9b5f30ebb/36bd6d07a402aa10-bc/s400x600/9f1b573bc3aea19c94bfca9089506f4d7a235daa.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/17d1bd3f4bee811a2df25fa9b5f30ebb/36bd6d07a402aa10-bc/s500x750/eed73845e002f9bfc3eda7dfd0411f806464891a.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/17d1bd3f4bee811a2df25fa9b5f30ebb/36bd6d07a402aa10-bc/s540x810/7377c7a0b27df387fe924e95840c8372555ed8fe.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/17d1bd3f4bee811a2df25fa9b5f30ebb/36bd6d07a402aa10-bc/s640x960/fb0b9d01bd8bdc2ff17dc54aa0cf787713f82017.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/17d1bd3f4bee811a2df25fa9b5f30ebb/36bd6d07a402aa10-bc/s1280x1920/03ba424f60ca8e933b5987a0625b2384159c42c7.jpg 1280w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/17d1bd3f4bee811a2df25fa9b5f30ebb/36bd6d07a402aa10-bc/s2048x3072/0772c91825f523b3cd465e53f328904470746cb2.jpg 1800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"/>"
