      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/73d3219ff78af14e5d9408ad65e6ad68/43ebea9371027255-50/s640x960/ed3c8753e4689ccddc229614661e1e5b316f5136.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"997\" data-orig-width=\"1500\" alt=\"Title: &quot;In shops now: Classic literature with added mathematics!&quot;&#10;&#10;Image: Four book covers.&#10;&#10;The Prime Number of Miss Jean Brodie, by Muriel Spark.&#10;Empire of the Sum, by JG Ballard.&#10;Wuthering Heights &#xC3;&#x97; lengths &#xC3;&#x97; widths, by Emily Bronte.&#10;The Remains Of the Data by Kazuo Ishiguro.\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/73d3219ff78af14e5d9408ad65e6ad68/43ebea9371027255-50/s75x75_c1/0fb22dbdb2c43a573d2f043ba3b13facab06477a.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/73d3219ff78af14e5d9408ad65e6ad68/43ebea9371027255-50/s100x200/94fb98d6b4d4a865fbe8a79db499b927861053b6.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/73d3219ff78af14e5d9408ad65e6ad68/43ebea9371027255-50/s250x400/948941d3f53c5a24bad400b67fd5386e55b43bdf.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/73d3219ff78af14e5d9408ad65e6ad68/43ebea9371027255-50/s400x600/bc6a03ef17904c76e23e1fb100a2881155e9d33c.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/73d3219ff78af14e5d9408ad65e6ad68/43ebea9371027255-50/s500x750/c8fcc77650ca7436b8f098211b0670a1dc08ba17.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/73d3219ff78af14e5d9408ad65e6ad68/43ebea9371027255-50/s540x810/07ad685b3f41b31e1c2be2a2b30cd11d6f98d533.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/73d3219ff78af14e5d9408ad65e6ad68/43ebea9371027255-50/s640x960/ed3c8753e4689ccddc229614661e1e5b316f5136.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/73d3219ff78af14e5d9408ad65e6ad68/43ebea9371027255-50/s1280x1920/3d260b10782dfc51c94a8b39f43e193f79cd5a28.jpg 1280w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/73d3219ff78af14e5d9408ad65e6ad68/43ebea9371027255-50/s2048x3072/f87fabbda8e09ef0836ea12d51941c0bb88fba81.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"/>"
