    {
      "id": "https://myjetpack.tumblr.com/post/820044039432945664",
      "url": "https://myjetpack.tumblr.com/post/820044039432945664",
      "title": "My latest cartoon for @guardian books",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/7e75e0e7a88505267847b110fc14b2c6/6396f8b967c8f20c-35/s640x960/a914800c48dce8bb8b7e008924edf0102c7bee21.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"779\" data-orig-width=\"1400\" alt=\"Title: The Cyclops discusses his part in Christopher Nolan's 'The Odyssey'   Panel 1. The cyclops wanders across his island, talking to the audience &quot;Most directors these days just use computers, so I appreciate that chris sailed the entire crew to a mythical island to shoot my scenes on film.&quot;  Panel 2. He continues as he climbs the hill. &quot;I wasn't going to do it: The young people are all so down on cannibalism. But I called up Homer and he said &quot;Are you an idiot?This is Hollywood money, not poetry royalties!&quot;  Panel 3. He sits on a rock and looks out to sea. &quot;So I got to meet Matt Damon, which was cool.&quot;\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/7e75e0e7a88505267847b110fc14b2c6/6396f8b967c8f20c-35/s75x75_c1/b2295022a16c291272714d7ec9cebf5148104dff.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/7e75e0e7a88505267847b110fc14b2c6/6396f8b967c8f20c-35/s100x200/5252b044b3ac6c61627ff9e8518aef1489367b19.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/7e75e0e7a88505267847b110fc14b2c6/6396f8b967c8f20c-35/s250x400/6cdd0748e1c8a8acb170f1a3f74a9994d7d3e700.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/7e75e0e7a88505267847b110fc14b2c6/6396f8b967c8f20c-35/s400x600/dea544b5488032bf1e3e97ff1fa2c23ea3f412ef.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/7e75e0e7a88505267847b110fc14b2c6/6396f8b967c8f20c-35/s500x750/5a4b1d875ca262b0faca9a420f3b7195da3e1d21.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/7e75e0e7a88505267847b110fc14b2c6/6396f8b967c8f20c-35/s540x810/6fd148c5799ede9c589ceab35097a4c944bcd480.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/7e75e0e7a88505267847b110fc14b2c6/6396f8b967c8f20c-35/s640x960/a914800c48dce8bb8b7e008924edf0102c7bee21.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/7e75e0e7a88505267847b110fc14b2c6/6396f8b967c8f20c-35/s1280x1920/78fc2357c0e2bd14e3e58ee376b793c692